 Exercises:
   - use_graph_arm=False is the default; results are byte-identical to the
     two-arm pipeline.
   - use_graph_arm=True surfaces BFS-reachable nodes via temporal fact-edges.
   - use_graph_arm type validation: non-bool raises TypeError.
